    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Luck &amp; Loot</strong> 是一款快节奏的<strong>骰子构筑 Roguelike</strong> 游戏，策略与混沌在此激烈碰撞。铸造你的<strong>专属骰子</strong>，驾驭<strong>狂野的战利品联动</strong>，深入<strong>腐化的埃卓利斯之境</strong>——每一次冒险，都是命运的又一次掷骰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在残酷的<strong>回合制战斗</strong>中智取凶残敌人，驾驭高风险修正，揭开这个轮回世界的黑暗秘辛。<strong>胜利将改变你，失败亦然。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208110/extras/bb9cf5a70ce23f543c4abc5a2da581ce.poster.avif?t=1771062150\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208110/extras/bb9cf5a70ce23f543c4abc5a2da581ce.webm?t=1771062150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208110/extras/bb9cf5a70ce23f543c4abc5a2da581ce.mp4?t=1771062150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场像素风格的对决中，对话如掷骰般铿锵有力，掷地有声。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >复古 Roguelike，融入骰子构筑的全新变奏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演三位英雄之一，他们皆为过往所困，皆在求索意义。在每一场九死一生的冒险中，<strong>用强大且可替换的骰面来定制你的骰子</strong>，铸就完美的构筑。每个抉择都至关重要，<strong>每次掷骰都关乎生死。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208110/extras/b7a88a49c9611adb03a19e4a5df45126.poster.avif?t=1771062150\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208110/extras/b7a88a49c9611adb03a19e4a5df45126.webm?t=1771062150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208110/extras/b7a88a49c9611adb03a19e4a5df45126.mp4?t=1771062150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个骰面都是抉择——铸就你的骰子，塑造你的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态骰子构筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用<strong>可替换、可强化的骰面</strong>来锻造你的策略，它们将决定你的力量——以及你的命运。<strong>献祭较弱的骰面以解锁强大的特质</strong>，并随着埃卓利斯的危险步步加深，<strong>随时调整你的构筑</strong>。但务必谨慎抉择： <strong>每枚骰子所能承载的力量有限，</strong> 而每个决定都将让你离掌控全局更近一步…… <strong>或是坠入深渊。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208110/extras/79f9ca2b5d8de5ce0074eca52b86ef36.poster.avif?t=1771062150\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208110/extras/79f9ca2b5d8de5ce0074eca52b86ef36.webm?t=1771062150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208110/extras/79f9ca2b5d8de5ce0074eca52b86ef36.mp4?t=1771062150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以色彩选择你的诅咒——每一种色彩方案，都是一抹新的厄运之色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >像素凶险 &amp; 芯片魔音</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入这个<strong>黑暗奇幻世界，每个像素都渗透着恐惧</strong>，<strong>每段芯片音乐都回荡着神话</strong>。Luck &amp; Loot 将<strong>复古风格</strong>与<strong>克苏鲁恐怖</strong>完美融合，邀您<strong>勇闯闹鬼森林、腐化城堡与诅咒旋律交织的领域</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将打破循环，<strong>还是成为虚无中的又一缕回响？</strong>骰子已经掷出。<strong>命运由你定夺。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 位英雄，各自拥有独特的骰面组合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 枚可不断自定义的骰子</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 座独特的地牢，每座都由一名强大的敌人主宰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ 种强大的骰子强化</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18+ 种灾厄修正</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ 种随机事件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ 种独特遗物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45+ 种敌人与Boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90+ 种可替换和强化的骰面</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽的可重玩性</p></li></ul>",
